00:36:20,801 --> 00:36:22,569
<font color=#FFFF00>sobre a vida após a morte...</font>

386
00:36:24,837 --> 00:36:26,373
<font color=#FFFF00>e eles deram-me esperança.</font>

387
00:36:27,873 --> 00:36:30,877
<font color=#FFFF00>Que talvez a vida continue
