390
00:36:39,386 --> 00:36:40,819
<font color=#FFFF00>"Querido pai"?</font>

391
00:36:40,821 --> 00:36:42,621
<font color=#FFFF00>Era uma coisa.</font>

392
00:36:42,623 --> 00:36:45,626
<font color=#FFFF00>Ele era o querido pai,
