425
00:41:57,804 --> 00:41:59,106
<font color=#FFFF00>Às vezes...</font>

426
00:42:00,105 --> 00:42:01,806
<font color=#FFFF00>Vejo coisas.</font>

427
00:42:01,808 --> 00:42:03,811
<font color=#FFFF00>Como a minha mãe vê coisas.</font>

428
00:42:08,081 --> 00:42:10,551
<font color=#FFFF00>Como fantasmas?</font>

429
00:42:15,355 --> 00:42:17,157
<font color=#FFFF00>Onde os vês?</font>

430
00:42:19,125 --> 00:42:20,761
<font color=#FFFF00>Onde quer que eu vá.</font>

431
00:42:27,100 --> 00:42:28,168
<font color=#FFFF00>Judy...</font>

432
00:42:29,868 --> 00:42:32,203
