00:44:48,976 --> 00:44:51,211
<font color=#FFFF00>Foi o que disseste antes.</font>

472
00:44:51,478 --> 00:44:52,809
<font color=#FFFF00>Sim.</font>

473
00:44:52,811 --> 00:44:55,045
<font color=#FFFF00>O meu pai diz
