525
00:48:21,955 --> 00:48:23,621
<font color=#FFFF00>sem o meu estúpido pai
ou alguém a interromper.</font>

526
00:48:23,623 --> 00:48:25,588
<font color=#FFFF00>Bob-Tem-Bolas!</font>

527
00:48:25,590 --> 00:48:27,994
<font color=#FFFF00>Boa.</font>

528
00:48:28,728 --> 00:48:30,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Os dois partilham pizza?</font>

529
00:48:32,197 --> 00:48:34,134
<font color=#FFFF00>- Devia ir buscar o dinheiro.
