545
00:49:12,638 --> 00:49:15,473
<font color=#FFFF00>Menos uma fatia.</font>

546
00:49:15,475 --> 00:49:17,641
<font color=#FFFF00>Gostei disso no carro.</font>

547
00:49:17,643 --> 00:49:19,012
<font color=#FFFF00>Até logo, Bolas.</font>

548
00:49:20,112 --> 00:49:22,512
<font color=#FFFF00>Convidava-te a entrar,
